Erubata oo lapolosak


1  “Ore lelo apolosak le Lawi, aa taa olosho pooki loo Lawi, meeta ninche erubata aashu enjung'ore tenebo Israel; lelo asarri oopejokini Olaitoriani te nkima einos ninche, o erubata enye. 
2   Meeta ninche enjung'ore tenebo ilalashera lenye; Olaitoriani ninye enjung'ore enye, anaa apa enaisiligie ninche. 
3  Naa keaku ena erubata oo lapolosak naing'uaa iltung'ana, neing'uaa nena kishorunot o lasar, aa olkiteng aashu enker, nchoo eisho ninche olapolosani orony o sederi pokira are o enkaya. 
4  O lng'anayio le dukuya le ntapa ino, o le naisho ino oo sabibu o le ilata ino, o lpapit le nkiterata oobarnuni te nker ino, nchoo ninye. 
5  Amu etegelua Olaitoriani Enkai ino ninye tiatua loshon linyi pooki, pee eitashe neisiaisho te nkarna o Laitoriani, ninye o layiok lenyena ntarasi.


6  “Naa tenelotu oltung'ani loo Lawi nkang'itie inyi eing'uaa Israel pooki, ine nemanya, naa keidim ninye aeu teneyieu, ine wueji negelu Olaitoriani, 
7  netum taa aisiaaisho te nkarna o Laitoriani Enkai enye, anaa ilkulikae tung'ana loo Lawi ooitashe aaisiaisho teine te dukuya Olaitoriani. 
8  Nchoo eitorisi irubat enye naainos, neng'amu erubata naing'uaa olmarei lenye.

Enkikoo tialo mbaa neme ine Nkai


9  “Tenilotu akenya ina kop nikincho Olaitoriani Enkai ino, milo ake aitamok kewan esujata e nena tabo o olminong le lelo oshon. 
10   Mincho ake etumi tiatua intae obo opejoo olayioni lenye aashu entito enye anaa olasar, o pooki ng'ae owosh isoito, anaa aibonisho, anaa amusoni, anaa olasakutoni, 
11   aashu oloo rasheta aashu olaenani, aashu olasakutoni, aashu oloirorie ilmeneng'a. 
12  Amu ore ilo oba anaa oloas kuna baa naa olminong to Laitoriani; naa ore enkaraki kuna baa olminong nearaa nena tabo Olaitoriani Enkai inyi aipang'ie te dukuya intae. 
13   Entaa ilemeeta entioto te dukuya Olaitoriani Enkai inyi. 
14  Amu ore kulo oshon letaa ilo aiwuang'ie naa kening lelo ooibonisho te ntorroni o oloomusu; kake ore iyie eitu kinyorraki Olaitoriani Enkai ino taasa ina.

Enkisiligata pee eirriuni oloiboni le Nkai


15   “Keputoki intae Olaitoriani Enkai inyi oloiboni leeijo nanu tiatua intae, tiatua ilalashera linyi, ilo intae entoning 
16  Anaa apa enitang'uarra to Laitoriani te Horeb teina olong e umata, ina kata apa pee ijo, ‘Mincho nanu aitoki aning oltoilo lo Laitoriani Enkai ai, aashu aigil adol ena kima kitok, maye ake.’ 
17  Naajoki nanu Olaitoriani, ‘Eiroro ninche aaitobiraki nena pooki naatejo ninche. 
18  Kaputoki nanu ninche oloiboni leeijo iyie tiatua ilalashera lenye; napik nanu irorei laainei atua enkutuk enye, neirorie ninye ninche nena pooki naitanap ninye. 
19   Ore ilo pooki lemening irorei laainei ooiroro ninye te nkarna ai, naitalaku nanu makewan te ninye. 
20  Kake ore ilo oiboni omusu airo irorei te nkarna ai leitu nanu aitanap ninye meiroro, aashu ilo oiro te nkarna e kulie aitin, ore ilo oiboni keye ake.’ 
21  Naa tenijo iyie to ltau lino, ‘Kaji iyiook kinko pee kiyiolou ororei leitu eiro Olaitoriani?’ 
22  Teneiro oloiboni te nkarna o Laitoriani, tenemelotu ilo rorei asipayu aashu aaku, ore ilo rorei mme Olaitoriani oiroro; oloiboni ake oiroro to lwuasa, nemiureyuyu intae ninye.

